title: Muuyu and ThinkPad Edge Take Yoga Digital
description: Matt Devine--yoga teacher and founder of Muuyu, one of the world's first online interactive eYoga platforms--describes how Muuyu and a ThinkPad Edge PC with the latest Intel Core processors are enabling yoga teachers and students to virtually practice yoga from any location.
